== Overview ==
The CyCorps Overseer class hover chassis is an upgraded version of the typical [[Overseer]] chassis, boasting higher starting technology levels and an additional module slot, making it one of the most advanced squad command units available.

The CyCorps Overseer is awarded to [[Controller|Controllers]] who have defeated the [[Master Controllers]] in [[Azra's Arena]] in [[Vulcore]].

